{"tid":2288851,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"告訴我，你父親為何不發表他的詩作？","createTime":"2020-11-16T22:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T02:53:00.000Z","uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9c351b6d4badeb36e62b6d7a3d0d65509f66c8","tid":2288851,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T22:17:05.000Z","msg":"因為他厭惡這個世界<br />\n<br />\n創造出美麗的詩句<br />\n<br />\n但拒絕發表，我認為這...<br />\n<br />\n這是他報復這世界的方式"},{"pid":"ab4e756094ee09c72528d026334a794bd2bbe96a","tid":2288851,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T22:18:42.000Z","msg":"你會因為憤怒而拒絕將作品公諸於世嗎？<br />\n<br />\n不，我不像我父親<br />\n<br />\n我告訴過你<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，我肯定人生"},{"pid":"77a6259c52ca59c4328bdca0dbaa5eb015fe03a9","tid":2288851,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T22:20:17.000Z","msg":"他為什麼如此<br />\n<br />\n厭惡人類？<br />\n<br />\n因為經歷幾千年文明<br />\n<br />\n人們仍學不懂如何去愛"},{"pid":"57fcd2c6b6355159a036784b54bf67b04a05d317","tid":2288851,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T22:24:13.000Z","msg":"Vicky Cristina Barcelona<br />\nDirector: Woody Allen<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0497465/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt0497465%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=61e953e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0497465/</a>"},{"pid":"448856becfd653fb67662b7d08be99da1fc05df2","tid":2288851,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdbb088b53a3b25e50d6f835e9d3060ca025371","tid":2288851,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T00:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f93d5a87911c0b81c4e17a798c24da149e04095","tid":2288851,"uid"